mpression that all levels in alt advancement cost the same exp as level 51. Then I saw a post where someone said it would costs 6 level 59s to get mastery in casting fury.  Once you get 6 ability points, does the exp change?  Will it now take me the same exp that it took to get through 55?  Or will the exp come just as easily as it did when I last got it? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarkaan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arkaan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/29/01 10:47:31 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://arkaan.dhs.org:88/eq/arksig.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about alt advancement</span><hr size=1> Whoever said that is nuts, an aaxp level is nowhere near lvl 59.  I am at level 56 and I would say aaxp is 4 or 5 times faster than regular 56 xp. <p><center>-----------------------------------------<br>
Baron Arkaan Riftwalker<br>56 Evoker<br>
Bristlebane</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujarnin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jarnin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/29/01 11:30:28 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.interofficenetworks.com/demo/doh/concussion.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about alt advancement</span><hr size=1> Level 51 for a Human Wizard = ~26,374,150 exp<br>
<br>
Level 59 for a Human Wizard = ~71,158,891 exp<br>
<br>
It takes 18(?) AA levels to get to level 3 of Spell casting mastery.<br>
<br>
18*26,374,150 = 474,734,700 exp<br>
<br>
474,734,700/71,158,891 = 6.6<br>
<br>
Thats how it works out. <p><center><IMG SRC=http://www.interofficenetworks.com/demo/doh/sigpic3.jpg><br><center><Br>Grand Master Fisherman<Br>Master Brewer<Br>Master Chef<Br>Master of Begging<Br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=40980">Check out my Gear</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uzupe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zupe</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/30/01 1:14:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about alt advancement</span><hr size=1> I truly think it is faster than 51 exp. I have been running 50/50 while in lvl 60 and have 1 yellow of normal exp and 3 yellows of alt. It is really fast is all you need to know. <p><B>******************</B><BR>

